Texts.Chs:
^orange;一年一度的节日大厅开放^reset; 

节日大厅再次向公众开放！ 快来与亲友一起在克里昂市外白雪皑皑的仙境中庆祝落地节。 与寻路者和他的朝圣徒见面，或参观伟大的节日之树拿起免费礼物！

对于国际游客，您可以使用克里昂使馆提供的公共交通工具轻松前往^green;节日大厅^reset;。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Opening of the annual Festival Hall^reset;

The Festival Hall opens its doors to the public yet again! Come and celebrate the Landing Festival with friends and family in a snowy wonderland just outside of Creon City. Meet the Pathfinder and his Pilgrims, or visit the great Festival Tree to pick up a free present!

For international visitors, you can easily travel to the Festival Hall using public transportation available at the Creon Embassy.
